---
// Economics section — the business case
---

<section id="economics" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-foggy-bg">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <h2 class="font-bold tracking-tight text-foggy-ink" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);">
      The economics.
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-[20px] text-foggy-ink-light leading-relaxed">
      Foggy doesn't have to build data centers, doesn't have to buy GPUs, and doesn't have to route data internationally. That's why the unit economics work in markets where the hyperscalers' don't.
    </p>

    <!-- Bank pilot example card -->
    <div class="mt-12 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-10">
      <h3 class="text-[20px] font-bold text-foggy-ink">A single bank pilot, sketched out</h3>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-4 text-[17px]">
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Customer profile</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">One bank, 1,000 call-center agents</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Calls processed</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">20 calls/agent/day × 5 min × 30 days</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Audio per month</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">3,000,000 minutes</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Foggy revenue</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">$36,000/month transcription</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Classification add-on</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">$3,450/month on 150M tx queries</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-slate-100 pb-2">
          <span class="text-foggy-ink-light">Total per customer</span>
          <span class="text-foggy-ink font-bold">~$475,000/year gross</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] italic text-foggy-ink-light">
        Roughly 30 large banks across Kenya, Rwanda, and Tanzania fit this profile. Sub-Saharan Africa cloud AI is a $3-4B market growing 27% annually (Fortune Business Insights).
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
